entries.description: Fixing exception using `RequestBody.fromInputStream` on non-resettable `InputStreams` by making `reset` conditional on `markSupported`. See [#1544](https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-java-v2/issues/1544) / [#1545](https://github.com/aws/aws-sdk-java-v2/issues/1545)
This release includes improvements and fixes bugs for the IAM Access Analyzer feature.
